# Replication package — what NOT to commit.
#
# Bulky, fully regenerable per-run outputs belong in the archived Zenodo
# deposit, not the git repository (reproduce.py recreates them deterministically).
data/raw/
*.log
__pycache__/
.venv/

# The repository-root .gitignore excludes "*.csv"; re-include the small
# processed/aggregate CSVs that the manuscript and reviewers actually need.
!data/processed/
!data/processed/**
